Audio files in this directory come from LibriVox (https://librivox.org/)
Like all contents provided by LibriVox, they are public domain.

Text files in this directory are manually extracted from https://www.ohchr.org/
They contain translations of the Universal Declaration of Human Rights in various languages.
The Office of the High Commissioner states these permissions for use:
    Permissions:
    If UDHR translations or materials are reproduced, users should make
    reference to this website as a source by providing a link.
     - Retrieved from https://www.ohchr.org/EN/UDHR/Pages/Introduction.aspx on 2020-03-20
